Package: regridR
Title: Re-Grid Raster Layers
Version: 0.1
Authors@R: person(given = c("A.", "Marcia"), 
                  family = "Barbosa", 
                  role = c("cre", "aut"), 
                  email = "ana.marcia.barbosa@gmail.com")
Description: This package can take a set of (possibly non-equal-area, e.g. lon-lat) raster layers, and a regular equal-area vector polygon grid (such as the EEA reference grid), and transforms the former to the same extent, resolution (i.e. equal-area pixels) and coordinate reference system as the latter. It also includes a function to download variables from web links, after checking if they already have been (fully) downloaded.
License: GPL (>=3)
Imports: terra
Encoding: UTF-8
